{"tid":863051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏】南韓傳媒報道，中國建築平均壽命只有約30年","createTime":"2018-10-15T10:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T13:47:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":111,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb448e73e2cc06e4bd201f8c1cf0109063cfd08","tid":863051,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"有南韓傳媒早前報道，指<span style=\"color: red;\">中國建築平均壽命只有約30年</span>，原因包括建築設計可被隨意修改、官員貪腐問題嚴重，以及中國政府要求建築物以「快餐式」方法建造。由此可見，中國豆腐渣工程聞名於世。近日內地網絡熱傳一段影片，見到一名男子拉住石造欄杆時，石柱竟突然斷裂，最終跌落河變成「落湯雞」。<br />\n<br />\n片段並沒有提及地點和時間，而影片拍到一名四眼男故意跨越護欄走在河邊斜坡，扮有型扶着石柱，繼而出力拉扯，讓身體向外傾斜，豈料他猛力拉住一欄杆時，石柱竟突然斷裂，男子失去重心跌落河。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181014/large/1539526792_eaf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181014%2Flarge%2F1539526792_eaf8.jpg&h=6780833c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181015/58794000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58794000&d=SU4NCEeP1Aeco5ACME9hRP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2a5630a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58794000&h=e828cfad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181015/58794000</a>"},{"pid":"d33418ca93fe8bb66b9321c5f231d7bd659f0b2f","tid":863051,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120f3f43908b60f97c32fcd7fae69cb31b85f9aa","tid":863051,"uid":52942,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"起咁穩點谷gdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d693ca46b2bca7b937622f31f1f376c3dd393280"